1
00:00:00,700 --> 00:00:01,935
You're different

2
00:00:02,802 --> 00:00:03,837
when you're with him.

3
00:00:05,605 --> 00:00:07,139
What's the deal between you two?

4
00:00:07,140 --> 00:00:08,375
I told you,

5
00:00:08,641 --> 00:00:09,641
there's nothing.

6
00:00:09,809 --> 00:00:11,344
But you're always looking out for him.

7
00:00:11,711 --> 00:00:12,412
Look,

8
00:00:12,412 --> 00:00:13,412
Bro,

9
00:00:14,514 --> 00:00:15,981
I've worked with plenty of people,

10
00:00:15,982 --> 00:00:17,350
but you've never cared this much.

11
00:00:17,951 --> 00:00:19,219
Why are you singling him out?

12
00:00:22,655 --> 00:00:23,723
Listen to me.

13
00:00:25,225 --> 00:00:26,626
Just keep him in check.

14
00:00:27,394 --> 00:00:28,560
I want him to know what it's like

15
00:00:28,561 --> 00:00:29,896
to actually need your help.

16
00:00:32,132 --> 00:00:32,966
Look, I don't know

17
00:00:32,967 --> 00:00:34,534
what your beef is with Chen Xiaoan,

18
00:00:35,535 --> 00:00:36,535
but be a man.

19
00:00:36,970 --> 00:00:38,681
If you have a problem,
deal with it yourself.

20
00:00:38,705 --> 00:00:39,906
Don't drag me into your mess.

21
00:00:50,950 --> 00:00:51,950
Alright, get ready.

22
00:00:57,957 --> 00:00:58,858
Hei Yan and Bai Xing,

23
00:00:58,858 --> 00:00:59,858
can we get

24
00:01:00,360 --> 00:01:01,560
a little more emotion, please?

25
00:01:01,928 --> 00:01:02,928
Now,

26
00:01:02,996 --> 00:01:03,797
for the jewelry...

27
00:01:03,797 --> 00:01:04,797
Right.

28
00:01:08,635 --> 00:01:09,735
Let's try a few more.

29
00:01:09,736 --> 00:01:11,237
Give me some eye contact.

30
00:01:12,839 --> 00:01:14,114
Sorry, can we
take a quick break?

31
00:01:14,674 --> 00:01:15,308
Okay, everyone.

32
00:01:15,309 --> 00:01:16,376
Let's take five.

33
00:01:17,503 --> 00:01:18,638
Who was it that said

34
00:01:19,145 --> 00:01:20,825
we shouldn't act like strangers next time?

35
00:01:21,614 --> 00:01:22,649
I'm not.

36
00:01:30,557 --> 00:01:31,658
Which one?

37
00:01:37,263 --> 00:01:38,263
This?

38
00:01:40,900 --> 00:01:41,900
Take it off.

39
00:01:51,845 --> 00:01:52,845
Before,

40
00:01:53,112 --> 00:01:54,681
you were on stage alone.

41
00:01:55,181 --> 00:01:56,181
But now,

42
00:01:56,649 --> 00:01:57,650
there are two of us.

43
00:02:00,453 --> 00:02:02,055
So keep your eyes on me.

44
00:02:22,108 --> 00:02:22,609
Okay.

45
00:02:22,610 --> 00:02:24,943
Alright, let's go again.

46
00:02:24,944 --> 00:02:26,111
Is everyone ready?

47
00:02:26,112 --> 00:02:27,247
Okay, once more.

48
00:02:27,480 --> 00:02:28,480
Get ready.

49
00:02:28,681 --> 00:02:29,849
And... action!
